OL,4,Cheat for Somerset man missing for a
OL,5,Cmonth
OL,7,FThe mother of a British man who has
OL,8,Fbeen lost in the Sardinian countryside
OL,9,Ffor a month says she won't give up in
OL,10,Fher search for him.
OL,12,FMichael Frison, 25, from Chard, went
OL,13,Ffor a walk in the Luras area of
OL,14,FNorthern Sardinia with a friend on 13
OL,15,FJuly.
OL,17,FHis friend returned while he decided
OL,18,Fto carry on, but when he didn't show
OL,19,Fup at night, she raised the alarm.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
