OL,7,FMichael's mother, Cristina Pittalis
OL,8,Fhas been hunting in 40C heat for him.
OL,10,F"I don't want to give up," she told
OL,11,FITV News. "I can't give up. That's
OL,12,Fabsolutely out of the question. There
OL,13,Fis no where I'm going back. If I stop
OL,14,Fsearching for my son, my personal
OL,15,Ffeeling, is that no one else will be
OL,16,Fout there looking for him."
OL,18,FMichael had no phone, laptop and few
OL,19,Fclothes with him when he went walking
OL,20,Fa month ago today.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
