OL,7,FAccording to his family, Michael's
OL,8,Ffriend returned back to their
OL,9,Faccommodation as he wanted to carry on
OL,10,Fwalking. When he failed to return that
OL,11,Fevening, she raised the alarm.
OL,13,FA police inquiry started and the
OL,14,F'Italian Hunters' search teams were
OL,15,Fcalled in, but there was no sign of
OL,16,FMichael.
OL,18,F"He really is a wonderful human
OL,19,Fbeing," said Cristina. "He is funny is
OL,20,Freally bright, is so intelligent most
OL,21,Fof all is so kind."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
