OL,7,FCristina said she was stunned by her
OL,8,Fson's disappearance.
OL,10,F"We had a very open communication
OL,11,Fbetween us, a very strong relationship
OL,12,Fand he did not hide the fact that he
OL,13,Fwanted to to stay in Sardinia. There
OL,14,Fis absolutely no reason for him not to
OL,15,Fcommunicate with me."
OL,17,FSardinia's Fire and Rescue Service -
OL,18,FVigili del Fuoco - has stood down
OL,19,Factive searches, leaving Cristina and
OL,20,Fher 10-year-old son alone in their
OL,21,Fhunt for Michael.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
