OL,7,FMichael's MP Adam Dance intervened in
OL,8,Fthe House of Commons. He told ITV
OL,9,FNews: "The searches had all been stood
OL,10,Fdown. So I immediately asked a
OL,11,Fquestion in the chamber in Parliament
OL,12,Fand I must say that the Minister was
OL,13,Fgreat meeting me within the day. I've
OL,14,Falso spoken with the Foreign Office to
OL,15,Ftry and get some action."
OL,17,FCristina is also being helped by a
OL,18,Fsmall team in Bristol - including
OL,19,Ffamily friend Claire.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
