OL,7,FClaire said: "You assume in the early
OL,8,Fdays that something is going to be
OL,9,Ffound or he would have been found
OL,10,Fphysically. So it is a worry. The main
OL,11,Fthing is the terrain, it's so vast.
OL,12,FAnd it's so hot out - over 40C."
OL,14,FInterpol and Avon and Somerset Police
OL,15,Fare both involved, but the Italian
OL,16,Fauthorities are leading on the inquiry.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
