OL,7,F"We all hope that he's he's surviving
OL,8,Fsomewhere in hiding out in in in the
OL,9,Fterrain somewhere. Yes. I mean, there
OL,10,Fare lots of posters up about him.
OL,11,FThere's lots on social media."
OL,13,FA Foreign, Commonwealth and
OL,14,FDevelopment Office spokesperson told
OL,15,FITV News: "We are supporting the
OL,16,Ffamily of a British man reported
OL,17,Fmissing in Sardinia and are in contact
OL,18,Fwith the local authorities."
